"use strict";(self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi=self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi||[]).push([[6461],{6461:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse("[{\"pageId\":1,\"rawText\":\"\u0130kinci S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0630\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u0650\\n\\n\u0130manda ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir saadet ve nimet ve ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir lezzet ve rahat bulundu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu temsil\xee hik\xe2yeci\u011fe bak, dinle:\\n\\nBir vakit iki adam, hem keyif hem ticaret i\xe7in seyahate giderler. Biri hodbin, t\xe2li\u2019siz bir tarafa; di\u011feri hud\xe2bin, bahtiyar di\u011fer tarafa s\xfcl\xfbk eder, giderler.\\n\\nHodbin adam, hem hodg\xe2m hem hod-endi\u015f hem bedbin oldu\u011fundan bedbinlik cezas\u0131 olarak nazar\u0131nda pek fena bir memlekete d\xfc\u015fer. Bakar ki her yerde \xe2ciz b\xee\xe7areler, zorba m\xfcthi\u015f adamlar\u0131n ellerinden ve tahribatlar\u0131ndan vaveyl\xe2 ediyorlar. B\xfct\xfcn gezdi\u011fi yerlerde b\xf6yle haz\xeen, el\xeem bir hali g\xf6r\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memleket, bir matemhane-i umum\xee \u015feklini alm\u0131\u015f. Kendisi \u015fu el\xeem ve muzlim haleti hissetmemek i\xe7in sarho\u015fluktan ba\u015fka \xe7are bulamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc herkes ona d\xfc\u015fman ve ecnebi g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor. Ve ortal\u0131kta dahi m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeleri ve meyusane a\u011flayan yetimleri g\xf6r\xfcr. Vicdan\u0131, azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri hud\xe2bin, hud\xe2-perest ve hak-endi\u015f, g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi ki nazar\u0131nda pek g\xfczel bir memlekete d\xfc\u015ft\xfc. \u0130\u015fte bu iyi adam, girdi\u011fi memlekette bir umum\xee \u015fenlik g\xf6r\xfcyor. Her tarafta bir s\xfcrur, bir \u015fehr\xe2yin, bir cezbe ve ne\u015fe i\xe7inde zikirhaneler; herkes ona dost ve akraba g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memlekette ya\u015fas\u0131nlar ve te\u015fekk\xfcrler ile bir terhisat-\u0131 umumiye \u015fenli\u011fi g\xf6r\xfcyor. Hem tekbir ve tehlil ile mesrurane ahz-\u0131 asker i\xe7in bir davul, bir muz\u0131ka sesi i\u015fitiyor. Evvelki bedbaht\u0131n hem kendi hem umum halk\u0131n elemi ile m\xfcteellim olmas\u0131na bedel; \u015fu bahtiyar, hem kendi hem umum halk\u0131n s\xfcruru ile mesrur ve m\xfcferrah olur. Hem g\xfczelce bir ticaret eline ge\xe7er, Allah\u2019a \u015f\xfckreder.\\n\\nSonra d\xf6ner, \xf6teki adama rast gelir. Halini anlar. Ona der: \u201cYahu sen divane olmu\u015fsun. B\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki \xe7irkinlikler, zahirine aksetmi\u015f olmal\u0131 ki g\xfclmeyi a\u011flamak, terhisat\u0131 soymak ve talan etmek tevehh\xfcm etmi\u015fsin. Akl\u0131n\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na al, kalbini temizle. T\xe2 \u015fu musibetli perde senin nazar\u0131ndan kalks\u0131n, hakikati g\xf6rebilesin. Zira nihayet derecede \xe2dil, merhametk\xe2r, raiyet-perver, muktedir, intizam-perver, m\xfc\u015ffik bir melikin memleketi hem bu derece g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcnde \xe2s\xe2r-\u0131 terakkiyat ve kemal\xe2t g\xf6steren bir memleket, senin vehminin g\xf6sterdi\u011fi surette olamaz.\u201d Sonra o bedbaht\u0131n akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na gelir, nedamet eder. \u201cEvet, ben i\u015fretten divane olmu\u015ftum. Allah senden raz\u0131 olsun ki cehennem\xee bir haletten beni kurtard\u0131n.\u201d der.\\n\\nEy nefsim! Bil ki evvelki adam k\xe2firdir veya f\xe2s\u0131k-\u0131 gafildir. \u015eu d\xfcnya, onun nazar\u0131nda bir matemhane-i umumiyedir. B\xfct\xfcn z\xeehayat, firak ve zeval sillesiyle a\u011flayan yetimlerdir. Hayvan ve insan ise ecel pen\xe7esiyle par\xe7alanan kimsesiz ba\u015f\u0131bozuklard\u0131r. Da\u011flar ve denizler gibi b\xfcy\xfck mevcudat, ruhsuz, m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeler h\xfckm\xfcndedirler. Daha bunun gibi \xe7ok el\xeem, ezici, deh\u015fetli evham, k\xfcfr\xfcnden ve dalaletinden ne\u015f\u2019et edip, onu manen tazip eder.\\n\\nDi\u011fer adam ise m\xfc\u2019mindir; Cenab-\u0131 H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131 tan\u0131r, tasdik eder. Onun nazar\u0131nda \u015fu d\xfcnya, bir zikirhane-i Rahman, bir talimg\xe2h-\u0131 be\u015fer ve hayvan ve bir meydan-\u0131 imtihan-\u0131 ins \xfc c\xe2nd\u0131r. B\xfct\xfcn vefiyat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye ise terhisatt\u0131r. Vazife-i hayat\u0131n\u0131 bitirenler, bu d\xe2r-\u0131 f\xe2niden, manen mesrurane, da\u011fda\u011fas\u0131z di\u011fer bir \xe2leme giderler. T\xe2 yeni vazifedarlara yer a\xe7\u0131ls\u0131n, gelip \xe7al\u0131\u015fs\u0131nlar. B\xfct\xfcn tevell\xfcdat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye ise ahz-\u0131 askere, silah alt\u0131na, vazife ba\u015f\u0131na gelmektir. B\xfct\xfcn z\xeehayat, birer muvazzaf mesrur asker, birer m\xfcstakim memnun memurlard\u0131r. B\xfct\xfcn sad\xe2lar ise ya vazife ba\u015flamas\u0131ndaki zikir ve tesbih ve paydostan gelen \u015f\xfck\xfcr ve tefrih veya i\u015flemek ne\u015fesinden ne\u015f\u2019et eden na\u011famatt\u0131r. B\xfct\xfcn mevcudat, o m\xfc\u2019minin nazar\u0131nda, Seyyid-i Ker\xeem\u2019inin ve M\xe2lik-i Rah\xeem\u2019inin birer munis hizmetk\xe2r\u0131, birer dost memuru, birer \u015firin kitab\u0131d\u0131r. Daha bunun gibi pek \xe7ok lat\xeef, ulvi ve leziz, tatl\u0131 hakikatler, iman\u0131ndan tecelli eder, tezah\xfcr eder.\",\"modernText\":\"\u0130kinci S\xf6z\\n\\n[[Bismillahirrahmanirrah\xeem|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahman ve Rahim olan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla. Esirgeyen ve ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla ba\u015flar\u0131m]]\\n\\n[[Onlar ki gayba inan\u0131rlar|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0630\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u0650|Onlar o kimselerdir ki, g\xf6rmedikleri halde y\xfcce yarat\u0131c\u0131ya ve iman hakikatlerine inan\u0131rlar (Bakara Suresi, 3. Ayet)]]\\n\\n\u0130manda ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[mutluluk|saadet|]] ve [[iyilik|nimet|Allah'\u0131n ihsan\u0131 olan l\xfctuf ve hediye]] ve ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[tad|lezzet|]] ve rahat bulundu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu [[\xf6rneklemeli|temsil\xee|benzetme ve k\u0131yas yoluyla hakikati anlatan]] hik\xe2yeci\u011fe bak, dinle:\\n\\nBir vakit iki adam, hem keyif hem ticaret i\xe7in seyahate giderler. Biri [[bencil|hodbin|kendini be\u011fenen, sadece kendi menfaatini d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen]], [[\u015fanss\u0131z|t\xe2li\u2019siz|]] bir tarafa; di\u011feri [[Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131yan|hud\xe2bin|her \u015feyde Allah'\u0131n r\u0131zas\u0131n\u0131 ve kudretini g\xf6ren]], [[mutlu|bahtiyar|\u015fansl\u0131 ve mesut]] di\u011fer tarafa [[gider|s\xfcl\xfbk eder|yol al\u0131r, o yola girer]], giderler.\\n\\n[[Bencil|Hodbin|]] adam, hem [[keyfine d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn|hodg\xe2m|sadece kendi zevk ve rahat\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen]] hem [[kendi \xe7\u0131kar\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen|hod-endi\u015f|ba\u015fkalar\u0131n\u0131 umursamadan sadece kendi gelece\u011fi i\xe7in endi\u015felenen]] hem [[karamsar|bedbin|her \u015feyi k\xf6t\xfc ve olumsuz g\xf6ren]] oldu\u011fundan [[karamsarl\u0131k|bedbinlik|]] cezas\u0131 olarak [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|nazar\u0131nda|g\xf6r\xfc\u015f a\xe7\u0131s\u0131nda, onun d\xfcnyas\u0131nda]] pek fena bir memlekete d\xfc\u015fer. Bakar ki her yerde [[g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz|\xe2ciz|]] [[\xe7aresizler|b\xee\xe7areler|]], zorba m\xfcthi\u015f adamlar\u0131n ellerinden ve tahribatlar\u0131ndan [[\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k at\u0131yorlar|vaveyl\xe2 ediyorlar|ac\u0131yla feryat edip inliyorlar]]. B\xfct\xfcn gezdi\u011fi yerlerde b\xf6yle [[h\xfcz\xfcnl\xfc|haz\xeen|]], [[ac\u0131kl\u0131|el\xeem|]] bir hali g\xf6r\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memleket, bir [[genel yas evi|matemhane-i umum\xee|herkesin yas tuttu\u011fu b\xfcy\xfck bir matem yeri]] \u015feklini alm\u0131\u015f. Kendisi \u015fu [[ac\u0131kl\u0131|el\xeem|]] ve [[karanl\u0131k|muzlim|]] [[durumu|haleti|]] [[duymamak i\xe7in|hissetmemek i\xe7in|]] sarho\u015fluktan ba\u015fka \xe7are bulamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc herkes ona d\xfc\u015fman ve [[yabanc\u0131|ecnebi|]] g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor. Ve ortal\u0131kta dahi m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeleri ve [[umutsuzca|meyusane|]] a\u011flayan yetimleri g\xf6r\xfcr. Vicdan\u0131, azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri [[Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131yan|hud\xe2bin|]], [[Allah'a ibadet eden|hud\xe2-perest|Allah'a kulluk eden ve O'na s\u0131\u011f\u0131nan]] ve [[do\u011frulu\u011fu d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen|hak-endi\u015f|hakk\u0131 ve hakikati g\xf6zeten]], g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi ki [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|nazar\u0131nda|]] pek g\xfczel bir memlekete d\xfc\u015ft\xfc. \u0130\u015fte bu iyi adam, girdi\u011fi memlekette bir [[genel|umum\xee|]] \u015fenlik g\xf6r\xfcyor. Her tarafta bir [[sevin\xe7|s\xfcrur|]], bir [[donanma \u015fenli\u011fi|\u015fehr\xe2yin|her taraf\u0131n \u0131\u015f\u0131klarla s\xfcslendi\u011fi b\xfcy\xfck bayram kutlamas\u0131]], bir [[kendinden ge\xe7me|cezbe|ilahi bir co\u015fkuyla kendinden ge\xe7me hali]] ve ne\u015fe i\xe7inde [[zikir yerleri|zikirhaneler|Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131n\u0131n an\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 ibadet yerleri]]; herkes ona dost ve akraba g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memlekette ya\u015fas\u0131nlar ve te\u015fekk\xfcrler ile bir [[genel terhis|terhisat-\u0131 umumiye|vazifesi bitenlerin serbest b\u0131rak\u0131lmas\u0131, genel g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lma bayram\u0131]] \u015fenli\u011fi g\xf6r\xfcyor. Hem [[Allah'\u0131n b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc anmak|tekbir|Allah\xfc Ekber diyerek O'nun y\xfcceli\u011fini ilan etmek]] ve [[Allah'\u0131n birli\u011fini s\xf6ylemek|tehlil|L\xe2 il\xe2he illallah diyerek Allah'\u0131n birli\u011fini zikretmek]] ile [[sevin\xe7le|mesrurane|]] [[askere al\u0131nma|ahz-\u0131 asker|vazife i\xe7in orduya \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lma]] i\xe7in bir davul, bir muz\u0131ka sesi i\u015fitiyor. Evvelki [[mutsuzun|bedbaht\u0131n|k\xf6t\xfc talihli ve mutsuz ki\u015finin]] hem kendi hem [[b\xfct\xfcn|umum|]] halk\u0131n elemi ile [[ac\u0131 \xe7ekmesine|m\xfcteellim olmas\u0131na|kederlenip elem duymas\u0131na]] bedel; \u015fu [[mutlu|bahtiyar|]], hem kendi hem [[b\xfct\xfcn|umum|]] halk\u0131n [[sevinci|s\xfcruru|]] ile [[mutlu|mesrur|]] ve [[ferahlar|m\xfcferrah olur|i\xe7ine huzur, ferahl\u0131k ve ayd\u0131nl\u0131k dolar]]. Hem g\xfczelce bir ticaret eline ge\xe7er, Allah\u2019a \u015f\xfckreder.\\n\\nSonra d\xf6ner, \xf6teki adama rast gelir. Halini anlar. Ona der: \u201cYahu sen divane olmu\u015fsun. [[i\xe7 d\xfcnyandaki|B\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki|]] \xe7irkinlikler, [[d\u0131\u015f d\xfcnyana|zahirine|d\u0131\u015f g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015f\xfcne ve d\u0131\u015f\u0131ndaki olaylara]] [[yans\u0131m\u0131\u015f olmal\u0131|aksetmi\u015f olmal\u0131|]] ki g\xfclmeyi a\u011flamak, [[g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lmay\u0131|terhisat\u0131|]] soymak ve talan etmek [[sanm\u0131\u015fs\u0131n|tevehh\xfcm etmi\u015fsin|kuruntuya d\xfc\u015f\xfcp \xf6yle hayal etmi\u015fsin]]. Akl\u0131n\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na al, kalbini temizle. T\xe2 \u015fu musibetli perde senin [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131ndan|nazar\u0131ndan|]] kalks\u0131n, hakikati g\xf6rebilesin. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira||*]] nihayet derecede [[adaletli|\xe2dil|]], [[merhametli|merhametk\xe2r|]], [[halk\u0131n\u0131 seven|raiyet-perver|halk\u0131n\u0131 koruyup g\xf6zetleyen ve \u015fefkatle himaye eden]], [[g\xfc\xe7l\xfc|muktedir|]], [[d\xfczen yanl\u0131s\u0131|intizam-perver|her \u015feyi yerli yerinde ve nizaml\u0131 yapan]], [[\u015fefkatli|m\xfc\u015ffik|]] bir [[h\xfck\xfcmdar\u0131n|melikin|]] memleketi hem bu derece g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcnde [[ilerleme eserleri|\xe2s\xe2r-\u0131 terakkiyat|geli\u015fme ve y\xfckselme belirtileri]] ve [[m\xfckemmellikler|kemal\xe2t|olgunluklar ve kusursuz g\xfczellikler]] g\xf6steren bir memleket, senin [[kuruntunun|vehminin|ger\xe7ek d\u0131\u015f\u0131 zann\u0131n\u0131n ve evham\u0131n\u0131n]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi surette olamaz.\u201d Sonra o [[mutsuzun|bedbaht\u0131n|]] akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na gelir, [[pi\u015fman olur|nedamet eder|]]. \u201cEvet, ben i\u015fretten divane olmu\u015ftum. Allah senden raz\u0131 olsun ki cehennem\xee bir [[durumdan|haletten|]] beni kurtard\u0131n.\u201d der.\\n\\nEy nefsim! Bil ki evvelki adam k\xe2firdir veya [[g\xfcnahk\xe2r ve duyars\u0131zd\u0131r|f\xe2s\u0131k-\u0131 gafildir|Allah'\u0131n emirlerini \xe7i\u011fneyen ve hakikatten habersiz ya\u015fayan gafildir]]. \u015eu d\xfcnya, onun [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|nazar\u0131nda|]] bir [[genel yas evidir|matemhane-i umumiyedir|]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[canl\u0131lar|z\xeehayat|]], [[ayr\u0131l\u0131k|firak|]] ve [[yok olu\u015f|zeval|bat\u0131\u015f, s\xf6nme ve son bulma]] [[tokad\u0131yla|sillesiyle|]] a\u011flayan yetimlerdir. Hayvan ve insan ise ecel pen\xe7esiyle par\xe7alanan kimsesiz ba\u015f\u0131bozuklard\u0131r. Da\u011flar ve denizler gibi b\xfcy\xfck [[varl\u0131klar|mevcudat|]], ruhsuz, m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeler h\xfckm\xfcndedirler. Daha bunun gibi \xe7ok [[ac\u0131kl\u0131|el\xeem|]], ezici, deh\u015fetli [[kuruntular|evham|]], k\xfcfr\xfcnden ve dalaletinden [[do\u011fup|ne\u015f\u2019et edip|kaynaklan\u0131p, ortaya \xe7\u0131k\u0131p]], onu manen [[azap verir|tazip eder|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131ya sokup manevi eziyet \xe7ektirir]].\\n\\nDi\u011fer adam ise [[inanan ki\u015fidir|m\xfc\u2019mindir|]]; [[Yarat\u0131c\u0131 olan Allah'\u0131|Cenab-\u0131 H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131|]] tan\u0131r, [[onaylar|tasdik eder|do\u011frulu\u011funu kabul edip kalp ile onaylar]]. Onun [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|nazar\u0131nda|]] \u015fu d\xfcnya, bir [[Rahman'\u0131n zikir yeri|zikirhane-i Rahman|Allah'\u0131n isimlerinin an\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve sanat\u0131n\u0131n sergilendi\u011fi bir ibadet yeri]], bir [[insanlar\u0131n e\u011fitim yeri|talimg\xe2h-\u0131 be\u015fer|]] ve hayvan ve bir [[insan ve cinlerin imtihan meydan\u0131d\u0131r|meydan-\u0131 imtihan-\u0131 ins \xfc c\xe2nd\u0131r|]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[hayvanlar\u0131n ve insanlar\u0131n \xf6l\xfcmleri|vefiyat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye|]] ise [[g\xf6revden terhistir|terhisatt\u0131r|]]. [[hayat g\xf6revini|Vazife-i hayat\u0131n\u0131|]] bitirenler, bu [[ge\xe7ici d\xfcnyadan|d\xe2r-\u0131 f\xe2niden|]], manen [[sevin\xe7le|mesrurane|]], [[s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131z|da\u011fda\u011fas\u0131z|g\xfcr\xfclt\xfcs\xfcz, karma\u015fadan uzak ve huzur i\xe7inde]] di\u011fer bir \xe2leme giderler. T\xe2 yeni [[g\xf6revlilere|vazifedarlara|]] yer a\xe7\u0131ls\u0131n, gelip \xe7al\u0131\u015fs\u0131nlar. B\xfct\xfcn [[hayvanlar\u0131n ve insanlar\u0131n do\u011fumlar\u0131|tevell\xfcdat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye|]] ise [[askere al\u0131nmaya|ahz-\u0131 askere|]], silah alt\u0131na, vazife ba\u015f\u0131na gelmektir. B\xfct\xfcn [[canl\u0131lar|z\xeehayat|]], birer [[g\xf6revli|muvazzaf|]] [[mutlu|mesrur|]] asker, birer [[do\u011fru|m\xfcstakim|]] memnun memurlard\u0131r. B\xfct\xfcn [[sesler|sad\xe2lar|]] ise ya vazife ba\u015flamas\u0131ndaki zikir ve [[Allah'\u0131 y\xfcceltme|tesbih|Allah'\u0131 noksan s\u0131fatlardan tenzih ederek anma]] ve paydostan gelen \u015f\xfck\xfcr ve [[sevinme|tefrih|ferahlama ve ne\u015felenme]] veya i\u015flemek ne\u015fesinden [[kaynaklanan|ne\u015f\u2019et eden|]] [[ezgilerdir|na\u011famatt\u0131r|melodiler, \u015fark\u0131lar ve tatl\u0131 seslerdir]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[varl\u0131klar|mevcudat|]], o [[inanan\u0131n|m\xfc\u2019minin|]] [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|nazar\u0131nda|]], [[C\xf6mert efendisinin|Seyyid-i Ker\xeem\u2019inin|Sonsuz l\xfctuf ve kerem sahibi olan Allah'\u0131n]] ve [[\u015eefkatli sahibinin|M\xe2lik-i Rah\xeem\u2019inin|Merhametli olan malikinin ve efendisinin]] birer [[cana yak\u0131n|munis|al\u0131\u015f\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, sevimli ve dost\xe7a]] hizmetk\xe2r\u0131, birer dost memuru, birer \u015firin kitab\u0131d\u0131r. Daha bunun gibi pek \xe7ok [[zarif|lat\xeef|ince ve g\xfczel]], [[y\xfcce|ulvi|]] ve [[lezzetli|leziz|]], tatl\u0131 hakikatler, iman\u0131ndan [[yans\u0131r|tecelli eder|belirir, parlar]], [[ortaya \xe7\u0131kar|tezah\xfcr eder|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr hale gelir]].\",\"processedBy\":\"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.17-17:21\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025.12.25-21:31\",\"oldText\":\"\u0130kinci S\xf6z\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Bismillahirrahmanirrah\xeem|Rahman ve Rahim olan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla. Esirgeyen ve ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla ba\u015flar\u0131m]]\\n\\n[[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0630\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u0650|Onlar ki gayba inan\u0131rlar|Onlar o kimselerdir ki, g\xf6rmedikleri halde y\xfcce yarat\u0131c\u0131ya ve iman hakikatlerine inan\u0131rlar (Bakara Suresi, 3. Ayet)]]\\n\\n\u0130manda ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[saadet|mutluluk]] ve [[nimet|iyilik|Allah'\u0131n ihsan\u0131 olan l\xfctuf ve hediye]] ve ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[lezzet|tad]] ve rahat bulundu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu [[temsil\xee|\xf6rneklemeli|benzetme ve k\u0131yas yoluyla hakikati anlatan]] hik\xe2yeci\u011fe bak, dinle:\\n\\nBir vakit iki adam, hem keyif hem ticaret i\xe7in seyahate giderler. Biri [[hodbin|bencil|kendini be\u011fenen, sadece kendi menfaatini d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen]], [[t\xe2li\u2019siz|\u015fanss\u0131z]] bir tarafa; di\u011feri [[hud\xe2bin|Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131yan|her \u015feyde Allah'\u0131n r\u0131zas\u0131n\u0131 ve kudretini g\xf6ren]], [[bahtiyar|mutlu|\u015fansl\u0131 ve mesut]] di\u011fer tarafa [[s\xfcl\xfbk eder|gider|yol al\u0131r, o yola girer]], giderler.\\n\\n[[Hodbin|Bencil]] adam, hem [[hodg\xe2m|keyfine d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn|sadece kendi zevk ve rahat\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen]] hem [[hod-endi\u015f|kendi \xe7\u0131kar\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen|ba\u015fkalar\u0131n\u0131 umursamadan sadece kendi gelece\u011fi i\xe7in endi\u015felenen]] hem [[bedbin|karamsar|her \u015feyi k\xf6t\xfc ve olumsuz g\xf6ren]] oldu\u011fundan [[bedbinlik|karamsarl\u0131k]] cezas\u0131 olarak [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda|g\xf6r\xfc\u015f a\xe7\u0131s\u0131nda, onun d\xfcnyas\u0131nda]] pek fena bir memlekete d\xfc\u015fer. Bakar ki her yerde [[\xe2ciz|g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz]] [[b\xee\xe7areler|\xe7aresizler]], zorba m\xfcthi\u015f adamlar\u0131n ellerinden ve tahribatlar\u0131ndan [[vaveyl\xe2 ediyorlar|\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k at\u0131yorlar|ac\u0131yla feryat edip inliyorlar]]. B\xfct\xfcn gezdi\u011fi yerlerde b\xf6yle [[haz\xeen|h\xfcz\xfcnl\xfc]], [[el\xeem|ac\u0131kl\u0131]] bir hali g\xf6r\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memleket, bir [[matemhane-i umum\xee|genel yas evi|herkesin yas tuttu\u011fu b\xfcy\xfck bir matem yeri]] \u015feklini alm\u0131\u015f. Kendisi \u015fu [[el\xeem|ac\u0131kl\u0131]] ve [[muzlim|karanl\u0131k]] [[haleti|durumu]] [[hissetmemek i\xe7in|duymamak i\xe7in]] sarho\u015fluktan ba\u015fka \xe7are bulamaz. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc herkes ona d\xfc\u015fman ve [[ecnebi|yabanc\u0131]] g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcyor. Ve ortal\u0131kta dahi m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeleri ve [[meyusane|umutsuzca]] a\u011flayan yetimleri g\xf6r\xfcr. Vicdan\u0131, azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri [[hud\xe2bin|Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131yan]], [[hud\xe2-perest|Allah'a ibadet eden|Allah'a kulluk eden ve O'na s\u0131\u011f\u0131nan]] ve [[hak-endi\u015f|do\u011frulu\u011fu d\xfc\u015f\xfcnen|hakk\u0131 ve hakikati g\xf6zeten]], g\xfczel ahl\xe2kl\u0131 idi ki [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda]] pek g\xfczel bir memlekete d\xfc\u015ft\xfc. \u0130\u015fte bu iyi adam, girdi\u011fi memlekette bir [[umum\xee|genel]] \u015fenlik g\xf6r\xfcyor. Her tarafta bir [[s\xfcrur|sevin\xe7]], bir [[\u015fehr\xe2yin|donanma \u015fenli\u011fi|her taraf\u0131n \u0131\u015f\u0131klarla s\xfcslendi\u011fi b\xfcy\xfck bayram kutlamas\u0131]], bir [[cezbe|kendinden ge\xe7me|ilahi bir co\u015fkuyla kendinden ge\xe7me hali]] ve ne\u015fe i\xe7inde [[zikirhaneler|zikir yerleri|Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131n\u0131n an\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 ibadet yerleri]]; herkes ona dost ve akraba g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. B\xfct\xfcn memlekette ya\u015fas\u0131nlar ve te\u015fekk\xfcrler ile bir [[terhisat-\u0131 umumiye|genel terhis|vazifesi bitenlerin serbest b\u0131rak\u0131lmas\u0131, genel g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lma bayram\u0131]] \u015fenli\u011fi g\xf6r\xfcyor. Hem [[tekbir|Allah'\u0131n b\xfcy\xfckl\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc anmak|Allah\xfc Ekber diyerek O'nun y\xfcceli\u011fini ilan etmek]] ve [[tehlil|Allah'\u0131n birli\u011fini s\xf6ylemek|L\xe2 il\xe2he illallah diyerek Allah'\u0131n birli\u011fini zikretmek]] ile [[mesrurane|sevin\xe7le]] [[ahz-\u0131 asker|askere al\u0131nma|vazife i\xe7in orduya \xe7a\u011fr\u0131lma]] i\xe7in bir davul, bir muz\u0131ka sesi i\u015fitiyor. Evvelki [[bedbaht\u0131n|mutsuzun|k\xf6t\xfc talihli ve mutsuz ki\u015finin]] hem kendi hem [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn]] halk\u0131n elemi ile [[m\xfcteellim olmas\u0131na|ac\u0131 \xe7ekmesine|kederlenip elem duymas\u0131na]] bedel; \u015fu [[bahtiyar|mutlu]], hem kendi hem [[umum|b\xfct\xfcn]] halk\u0131n [[s\xfcruru|sevinci]] ile [[mesrur|mutlu]] ve [[m\xfcferrah olur|ferahlar|i\xe7ine huzur, ferahl\u0131k ve ayd\u0131nl\u0131k dolar]]. Hem g\xfczelce bir ticaret eline ge\xe7er, Allah\u2019a \u015f\xfckreder.\\n\\nSonra d\xf6ner, \xf6teki adama rast gelir. Halini anlar. Ona der: \u201cYahu sen divane olmu\u015fsun. [[B\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki|i\xe7 d\xfcnyandaki]] \xe7irkinlikler, [[zahirine|d\u0131\u015f d\xfcnyana|d\u0131\u015f g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015f\xfcne ve d\u0131\u015f\u0131ndaki olaylara]] [[aksetmi\u015f olmal\u0131|yans\u0131m\u0131\u015f olmal\u0131]] ki g\xfclmeyi a\u011flamak, [[terhisat\u0131|g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lmay\u0131]] soymak ve talan etmek [[tevehh\xfcm etmi\u015fsin|sanm\u0131\u015fs\u0131n|kuruntuya d\xfc\u015f\xfcp \xf6yle hayal etmi\u015fsin]]. Akl\u0131n\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na al, kalbini temizle. T\xe2 \u015fu musibetli perde senin [[nazar\u0131ndan|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131ndan]] kalks\u0131n, hakikati g\xf6rebilesin. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc||*]] nihayet derecede [[\xe2dil|adaletli]], [[merhametk\xe2r|merhametli]], [[raiyet-perver|halk\u0131n\u0131 seven|halk\u0131n\u0131 koruyup g\xf6zetleyen ve \u015fefkatle himaye eden]], [[muktedir|g\xfc\xe7l\xfc]], [[intizam-perver|d\xfczen yanl\u0131s\u0131|her \u015feyi yerli yerinde ve nizaml\u0131 yapan]], [[m\xfc\u015ffik|\u015fefkatli]] bir [[melikin|h\xfck\xfcmdar\u0131n]] memleketi hem bu derece g\xf6z \xf6n\xfcnde [[\xe2s\xe2r-\u0131 terakkiyat|ilerleme eserleri|geli\u015fme ve y\xfckselme belirtileri]] ve [[kemal\xe2t|m\xfckemmellikler|olgunluklar ve kusursuz g\xfczellikler]] g\xf6steren bir memleket, senin [[vehminin|kuruntunun|ger\xe7ek d\u0131\u015f\u0131 zann\u0131n\u0131n ve evham\u0131n\u0131n]] g\xf6sterdi\u011fi surette olamaz.\u201d Sonra o [[bedbaht\u0131n|mutsuzun]] akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na gelir, [[nedamet eder|pi\u015fman olur]]. \u201cEvet, ben i\u015fretten divane olmu\u015ftum. Allah senden raz\u0131 olsun ki cehennem\xee bir [[haletten|durumdan]] beni kurtard\u0131n.\u201d der.\\n\\nEy nefsim! Bil ki evvelki adam k\xe2firdir veya [[f\xe2s\u0131k-\u0131 gafildir|g\xfcnahk\xe2r ve duyars\u0131zd\u0131r|Allah'\u0131n emirlerini \xe7i\u011fneyen ve hakikatten habersiz ya\u015fayan gafildir]]. \u015eu d\xfcnya, onun [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda]] bir [[matemhane-i umumiyedir|genel yas evidir]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[z\xeehayat|canl\u0131lar]], [[firak|ayr\u0131l\u0131k]] ve [[zeval|yok olu\u015f|bat\u0131\u015f, s\xf6nme ve son bulma]] [[sillesiyle|tokad\u0131yla]] a\u011flayan yetimlerdir. Hayvan ve insan ise ecel pen\xe7esiyle par\xe7alanan kimsesiz ba\u015f\u0131bozuklard\u0131r. Da\u011flar ve denizler gibi b\xfcy\xfck [[mevcudat|varl\u0131klar]], ruhsuz, m\xfcthi\u015f cenazeler h\xfckm\xfcndedirler. Daha bunun gibi \xe7ok [[el\xeem|ac\u0131kl\u0131]], ezici, deh\u015fetli [[evham|kuruntular]], k\xfcfr\xfcnden ve dalaletinden [[ne\u015f\u2019et edip|do\u011fup|kaynaklan\u0131p, ortaya \xe7\u0131k\u0131p]], onu manen [[tazip eder|azap verir|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131ya sokup manevi eziyet \xe7ektirir]].\\n\\nDi\u011fer adam ise [[m\xfc\u2019mindir|inanan ki\u015fidir]]; [[Cenab-\u0131 H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131|Yarat\u0131c\u0131 olan Allah'\u0131]] tan\u0131r, [[tasdik eder|onaylar|do\u011frulu\u011funu kabul edip kalp ile onaylar]]. Onun [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda]] \u015fu d\xfcnya, bir [[zikirhane-i Rahman|Rahman'\u0131n zikir yeri|Allah'\u0131n isimlerinin an\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve sanat\u0131n\u0131n sergilendi\u011fi bir ibadet yeri]], bir [[talimg\xe2h-\u0131 be\u015fer|insanlar\u0131n e\u011fitim yeri]] ve hayvan ve bir [[meydan-\u0131 imtihan-\u0131 ins \xfc c\xe2nd\u0131r|insan ve cinlerin imtihan meydan\u0131d\u0131r]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[vefiyat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye|hayvanlar\u0131n ve insanlar\u0131n \xf6l\xfcmleri]] ise [[terhisatt\u0131r|g\xf6revden terhistir]]. [[Vazife-i hayat\u0131n\u0131|hayat g\xf6revini]] bitirenler, bu [[d\xe2r-\u0131 f\xe2niden|ge\xe7ici d\xfcnyadan]], manen [[mesrurane|sevin\xe7le]], [[da\u011fda\u011fas\u0131z|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131z|g\xfcr\xfclt\xfcs\xfcz, karma\u015fadan uzak ve huzur i\xe7inde]] di\u011fer bir \xe2leme giderler. T\xe2 yeni [[vazifedarlara|g\xf6revlilere]] yer a\xe7\u0131ls\u0131n, gelip \xe7al\u0131\u015fs\u0131nlar. B\xfct\xfcn [[tevell\xfcdat-\u0131 hayvaniye ve insaniye|hayvanlar\u0131n ve insanlar\u0131n do\u011fumlar\u0131]] ise [[ahz-\u0131 askere|askere al\u0131nmaya]], silah alt\u0131na, vazife ba\u015f\u0131na gelmektir. B\xfct\xfcn [[z\xeehayat|canl\u0131lar]], birer [[muvazzaf|g\xf6revli]] [[mesrur|mutlu]] asker, birer [[m\xfcstakim|do\u011fru]] memnun memurlard\u0131r. B\xfct\xfcn [[sad\xe2lar|sesler]] ise ya vazife ba\u015flamas\u0131ndaki zikir ve [[tesbih|Allah'\u0131 y\xfcceltme|Allah'\u0131 noksan s\u0131fatlardan tenzih ederek anma]] ve paydostan gelen \u015f\xfck\xfcr ve [[tefrih|sevinme|ferahlama ve ne\u015felenme]] veya i\u015flemek ne\u015fesinden [[ne\u015f\u2019et eden|kaynaklanan]] [[na\u011famatt\u0131r|ezgilerdir|melodiler, \u015fark\u0131lar ve tatl\u0131 seslerdir]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[mevcudat|varl\u0131klar]], o [[m\xfc\u2019minin|inanan\u0131n]] [[nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131nda]], [[Seyyid-i Ker\xeem\u2019inin|C\xf6mert efendisinin|Sonsuz l\xfctuf ve kerem sahibi olan Allah'\u0131n]] ve [[M\xe2lik-i Rah\xeem\u2019inin|\u015eefkatli sahibinin|Merhametli olan malikinin ve efendisinin]] birer [[munis|cana yak\u0131n|al\u0131\u015f\u0131lm\u0131\u015f, sevimli ve dost\xe7a]] hizmetk\xe2r\u0131, birer dost memuru, birer \u015firin kitab\u0131d\u0131r. Daha bunun gibi pek \xe7ok [[lat\xeef|zarif|ince ve g\xfczel]], [[ulvi|y\xfcce]] ve [[leziz|lezzetli]], tatl\u0131 hakikatler, iman\u0131ndan [[tecelli eder|yans\u0131r|belirir, parlar]], [[tezah\xfcr eder|ortaya \xe7\u0131kar|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr hale gelir]].\"},{\"pageId\":2,\"rawText\":\"Demek iman, bir manev\xee t\xfbba-i cennet \xe7ekirde\u011fini ta\u015f\u0131yor. K\xfcf\xfcr ise manev\xee bir zakkum-u cehennem tohumunu sakl\u0131yor.\\n\\nDemek sel\xe2met ve emniyet, yaln\u0131z \u0130sl\xe2miyet\u2019te ve imandad\u0131r. \xd6yle ise biz daima \u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u062f\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 demeliyiz.\\n\\n***\",\"modernText\":\"Demek [[inan\xe7|iman|Allah'a ve O'nun bildirdiklerine \u015f\xfcphesiz inanma]], bir [[maddi olmayan|manev\xee|g\xf6zle g\xf6r\xfclmeyen, ruha ve manaya ait]] [[cennet t\xfbba a\u011fac\u0131|t\xfbba-i cennet|Cennette bulunan, k\xf6k\xfc yukar\u0131da dallar\u0131 a\u015fa\u011f\u0131da, her t\xfcrl\xfc meyveyi veren muazzam a\u011fa\xe7]] \xe7ekirde\u011fini ta\u015f\u0131yor. [[inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k|K\xfcf\xfcr|Allah'\u0131 ink\xe2r etme, imans\u0131zl\u0131k]] ise [[maddi olmayan|manev\xee|ruha ve manaya ait]] bir [[cehennem zakkum a\u011fac\u0131|zakkum-u cehennem|Cehennemde yeti\u015fen, meyvesi \xe7ok ac\u0131, \u015feytanlar\u0131n ba\u015flar\u0131na benzeyen ve azap veren a\u011fa\xe7]] tohumunu sakl\u0131yor.\\n\\nDemek [[kurtulu\u015f|sel\xe2met|esenlik, her t\xfcrl\xfc korku, keder ve tehlikeden emin olma]] ve [[g\xfcven|emniyet|korkusuzluk, emniyet i\xe7inde olma hali]], yaln\u0131z \u0130sl\xe2miyet\u2019te ve imandad\u0131r. \xd6yle ise biz [[her zaman|daima|s\xfcrekli]] [[\u0130slam dini ve iman\u0131n m\xfckemmelli\u011fi (taml\u0131\u011f\u0131) \xfczerine bize bu nimetleri verdi\u011fi i\xe7in Allah'a hamdolsun|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u062f\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650|]] demeliyiz.\\n\\n***\",\"processedBy\":\"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.17-17:21\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025.12.25-21:31\",\"oldText\":\"Demek [[iman|inan\xe7|Allah'a ve O'nun bildirdiklerine \u015f\xfcphesiz inanma]], bir [[manev\xee|maddi olmayan|g\xf6zle g\xf6r\xfclmeyen, ruha ve manaya ait]] [[t\xfbba-i cennet|cennet t\xfbba a\u011fac\u0131|Cennette bulunan, k\xf6k\xfc yukar\u0131da dallar\u0131 a\u015fa\u011f\u0131da, her t\xfcrl\xfc meyveyi veren muazzam a\u011fa\xe7]] \xe7ekirde\u011fini ta\u015f\u0131yor. [[K\xfcf\xfcr|inan\xe7s\u0131zl\u0131k|Allah'\u0131 ink\xe2r etme, imans\u0131zl\u0131k]] ise [[manev\xee|maddi olmayan|ruha ve manaya ait]] bir [[zakkum-u cehennem|cehennem zakkum a\u011fac\u0131|Cehennemde yeti\u015fen, meyvesi \xe7ok ac\u0131, \u015feytanlar\u0131n ba\u015flar\u0131na benzeyen ve azap veren a\u011fa\xe7]] tohumunu sakl\u0131yor.\\n\\nDemek [[sel\xe2met|kurtulu\u015f|esenlik, her t\xfcrl\xfc korku, keder ve tehlikeden emin olma]] ve [[emniyet|g\xfcven|korkusuzluk, emniyet i\xe7inde olma hali]], yaln\u0131z \u0130sl\xe2miyet\u2019te ve imandad\u0131r. \xd6yle ise biz [[daima|her zaman|s\xfcrekli]] [[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u062f\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0656\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650|\u0130slam dini ve iman\u0131n m\xfckemmelli\u011fi (taml\u0131\u011f\u0131) \xfczerine bize bu nimetleri verdi\u011fi i\xe7in Allah'a hamdolsun]] demeliyiz.\\n\\n***\"}]")}}]);